---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Student KITAS (E30A) Support" description="Secure your family's future in Bali with our expert Student KITAS support. Enroll in top schools and build a life of adventure.">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative py-32 px-6 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
            <img src="/images/gallery/medium-shot-kids-sitting-together-table.jpg" class="w-full h-full object-cover brightness-50" alt="Kids in Bali" />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-sunny-charcoal/40 to-sunny-charcoal/80"></div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto relative z-10 text-center">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-7xl font-heading font-bold text-white mb-8 leading-tight">
                Turn Bali from a Holiday into a <br/>
                <span class="text-sunny-yellow italic">Childhood to Cherish Forever</span>
            </h1>
            <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-sunny-cream mb-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                Now Offering Expert Student KITAS (E30A) Support – Enroll Your Child in Bali's Inspiring Schools and Build a Life of Adventure, Learning, and Family Memories
            </h2>
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-200 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed mb-12">
                Bali isn't just a destination—it's a living classroom where curiosity meets nature, play sparks creativity, and every day builds resilience and wonder. Our dedicated Student Visa support helps families like yours transition from short visits to meaningful, long-term living. By enrolling your child in an accredited, child-centered program, secure a legal Student KITAS for them and Dependent KITAS for parents—giving your family stability, cultural immersion, and the freedom to truly belong.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center items-center">
                <a href="https://wa.me/628113801905" target="_blank" class="bg-sunny-yellow text-sunny-charcoal px-10 py-5 rounded-full text-xl font-bold hover:scale-110 transition-transform shadow-xl flex items-center gap-3">
                    <span class="text-2xl">📱</span> Message on WhatsApp
                </a>
                <a href="/visa-consultation" class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md text-white border-2 border-white/20 px-10 py-5 rounded-full text-xl font-bold hover:bg-white/20 transition-all">
                    Fill Consultation Form
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Benefits Section -->
    <section class="py-24 px-6 md:px-12 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-sunny-charcoal mb-6">Why Choose Student KITAS for Your Family in Bali?</h2>
                <div class="w-24 h-2 bg-sunny-yellow mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <!-- Benefit 1 -->
                <div class="bg-sunny-cream/30 p-8 rounded-3xl border-2 border-sunny-blue/10 hover:border-sunny-blue/30 transition-all hover:shadow-xl group">
                    <div class="text-4xl mb-6 group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform inline-block">🏝️</div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-sunny-blue">Unforgettable Childhood Experiences</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Watch your child thrive through hands-on learning in Bali's jungles, beaches, rice terraces, and nature-based or international programs—fostering creativity, independence, global awareness, and a deep connection to the world.</p>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Benefit 2 -->
                <div class="bg-sunny-cream/30 p-8 rounded-3xl border-2 border-sunny-yellow/10 hover:border-sunny-yellow/30 transition-all hover:shadow-xl group">
                    <div class="text-4xl mb-6 group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform inline-block">📜</div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-sunny-yellow">Secure, Legal Long-Term Residency</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Obtain a Student KITAS (E30A) for your child (typically 1–2 years initial, renewable with continued enrollment, up to several years total) plus Dependent KITAS for parents—eliminate stressful visa runs and enjoy multiple-entry freedom.</p>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Benefit 3 -->
                <div class="bg-sunny-cream/30 p-8 rounded-3xl border-2 border-sunny-green/10 hover:border-sunny-green/30 transition-all hover:shadow-xl group">
                    <div class="text-4xl mb-6 group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform inline-block">🎓</div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-sunny-green">Personalized Education Pathways</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">We guide you to the perfect fit: Reggio Emilia-inspired kindergartens, nature-focused preschools, or international schools tailored to your child's age, your family's values, and long-term goals.</p>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Benefit 4 -->
                <div class="bg-sunny-cream/30 p-8 rounded-3xl border-2 border-sunny-blue/10 hover:border-sunny-blue/30 transition-all hover:shadow-xl group">
                    <div class="text-4xl mb-6 group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform inline-block">🏠</div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-sunny-blue">True Family-Centered Living</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Gain the gift of time—more shared moments exploring temples, wellness retreats, markets, and adventures—without the limitations of tourist visas or constant border hopping.</p>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Benefit 5 -->
                <div class="bg-sunny-cream/30 p-8 rounded-3xl border-2 border-sunny-yellow/10 hover:border-sunny-yellow/30 transition-all hover:shadow-xl group">
                    <div class="text-4xl mb-6 group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform inline-block">🤝</div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-sunny-yellow">Hassle-Free, Expert Guidance</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">From school matching and enrollment to full document preparation, sponsorship coordination, and immigration submission—we manage the complexities so you can focus on embracing Bali life.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How It Works Section -->
    <section class="py-24 px-6 md:px-12 bg-sunny-cream/20">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
            <div class="text-center mb-20">
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-sunny-charcoal mb-6">How It Works – Simple 4-Step Process</h2>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Your journey from holiday to home, simplified with our expert support.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="space-y-12">
                <!-- Step 1 -->
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center bg-white p-8 rounded-4xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                    <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-sunny-blue text-white rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-4xl font-bold shrink-0">1</div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-sunny-charcoal">Free Initial Consultation</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">Schedule a no-obligation call or chat to discuss your family's situation, child's age, preferred learning style, and eligibility for Student KITAS.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Step 2 -->
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center bg-white p-8 rounded-4xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                    <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-sunny-yellow text-white rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-4xl font-bold shrink-0">2</div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-sunny-charcoal">School Matching & Enrollment Support</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">Receive curated recommendations for accredited, sponsor-eligible programs in Bali. We assist with applications and secure the essential Letter of Acceptance.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Step 3 -->
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center bg-white p-8 rounded-4xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                    <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-sunny-green text-white rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-4xl font-bold shrink-0">3</div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-sunny-charcoal">Visa & KITAS Application</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">Full-service preparation: gather documents, coordinate school sponsorship, submit for the child's Student KITAS (E30A) and parents' Dependent KITAS. We handle follow-ups with immigration.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Step 4 -->
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center bg-white p-8 rounded-4xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                    <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-sunny-blue text-white rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-4xl font-bold shrink-0">4</div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-sunny-charcoal">Arrival, Orientation & Ongoing Support</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">Smooth transition help—including settling-in tips, local resources, and renewal guidance for continued stays.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="mt-16 p-8 bg-sunny-charcoal/5 rounded-3xl border border-sunny-charcoal/10 italic text-sm text-gray-500">
                <p><strong>Important Note:</strong> Visa and KITAS approvals are at the sole discretion of Indonesian Immigration authorities. Requirements (including school sponsorship and documentation) can change; we provide professional assistance based on current regulations (as of 2026), but cannot guarantee outcomes. School enrollment fees are separate from our visa support services.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section class="py-24 px-6 md:px-12 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-sunny-charcoal mb-6">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
                <div class="w-24 h-2 bg-sunny-green mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <details class="group bg-sunny-cream/20 rounded-3xl p-6 border-2 border-transparent hover:border-sunny-blue/20 transition-all cursor-pointer">
                    <summary class="text-xl font-bold list-none flex justify-between items-center text-sunny-charcoal">
                        What ages qualify for Student KITAS?
                        <span class="text-sunny-blue group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
                    </summary>
                    <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Typically from nursery/kindergarten age (around 3+ years), though some programs accept younger children if accredited and sponsor-eligible. We assess your case individually.</p>
                </details>

                <details class="group bg-sunny-cream/20 rounded-3xl p-6 border-2 border-transparent hover:border-sunny-yellow/20 transition-all cursor-pointer">
                    <summary class="text-xl font-bold list-none flex justify-between items-center text-sunny-charcoal">
                        Can both parents (or siblings) join as dependents?
                        <span class="text-sunny-yellow group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
                    </summary>
                    <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Yes—in most cases, both parents can apply for Dependent KITAS under the child's school sponsorship. Siblings may also qualify depending on the setup and school policy.</p>
                </details>

                <details class="group bg-sunny-cream/20 rounded-3xl p-6 border-2 border-transparent hover:border-sunny-green/20 transition-all cursor-pointer">
                    <summary class="text-xl font-bold list-none flex justify-between items-center text-sunny-charcoal">
                        How long can we stay?
                        <span class="text-sunny-green group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
                    </summary>
                    <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Initial Student KITAS often 1–2 years (some options up to 4 years in 2026); renewable with ongoing enrollment, potentially for several years total before reassessment.</p>
                </details>

                <details class="group bg-sunny-cream/20 rounded-3xl p-6 border-2 border-transparent hover:border-sunny-blue/20 transition-all cursor-pointer">
                    <summary class="text-xl font-bold list-none flex justify-between items-center text-sunny-charcoal">
                        What happens if the application is delayed or denied?
                        <span class="text-sunny-blue group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
                    </summary>
                    <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">We provide transparent guidance, help with appeals where possible, and explore alternative family-friendly visa pathways to minimize any disruption.</p>
                </details>

                <details class="group bg-sunny-cream/20 rounded-3xl p-6 border-2 border-transparent hover:border-sunny-yellow/20 transition-all cursor-pointer">
                    <summary class="text-xl font-bold list-none flex justify-between items-center text-sunny-charcoal">
                        Do we need to leave Indonesia during processing?
                        <span class="text-sunny-yellow group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
                    </summary>
                    <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Many families apply from within Bali on a valid existing visa; we advise on the best timing to avoid status gaps.</p>
                </details>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Call-to-Action Section -->
    <section class="py-24 px-6 md:px-12 bg-sunny-blue text-white overflow-hidden relative">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-10">
            <img src="/images/gallery/outdoor-play.jpg" class="w-full h-full object-cover" alt="Background" />
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto relative z-10 text-center">
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-heading font-bold mb-8">Ready to Make Bali Part of Your <span class="text-sunny-yellow italic">Child's Story?</span></h2>
            <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl mb-12 text-blue-100">Book Your Free Consultation Today and Start Building Lifelong Memories.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-6">
                <a href="https://wa.me/628113801905" target="_blank" class="bg-sunny-yellow text-sunny-charcoal px-12 py-6 rounded-full text-2xl font-bold hover:scale-110 transition-transform inline-flex items-center gap-4 shadow-2xl">
                    Message us on WhatsApp: +62 811-3801-905
                </a>
                <p class="text-lg text-blue-200">Or <a href="/visa-consultation" class="underline hover:text-white transition-colors">fill out our specialized form</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
